			<description><![CDATA[<p>
We are looking for a front-end and mobile developer to help us build our next-generation multi-platform video publishing solutions.</p>
<p>
Our job is to help our customers publish their video content on any device, anywhere in the world. You will have the opportunity to work in a diverse field of content management solutions, mobile websites, mobile apps and ConnectedTVs.</p>
<p>
Your responsibilities will include creating new video player concepts and user interfaces, designing and implementing web-based user-interfaces and integrating our publishing technology with existing content management and ad serving platforms.</p>
<p>
You must be prepared to work with a set of different technologies and languages including iOS, Android, Windows Phone, Javascript, Actionscript, HTML5, CSS, JQuery, GWT, Ajax and JSON.</p>
<p>
The ideal candidate we are looking for</p>
<ul>
<li>
has a start-up attitude and wants to be part of a great story</li>
<li>
has the flexibility required by a fast-paced, constantly evolving environment</li>
<li>
has experience in developing multi-platform applications and user interfaces</li>
</ul>
<p>
Knowledge of video and streaming technologies is a plus.</p>
<p>
The position offers a compensation package consisting of salary and stock options. Other benefits include a mobile phone, health care plan and paid holidays.</p>
<p>
About ThirdPresence</p>
<p>
ThirdPresence is a cloud-based Software-as-a-Service (SaaS) platform that enables media companies and online video publishers to stream video-on-demand, podcasts and live video content to any video-capable mobile phone or tablet, including the Apple iPhone, iPad, Android, BlackBerry and Windows Phone &ndash;based devices. ThirdPresence also enables monetization of the content either by advertising, subscription or pay-per-view, and provides detailed tracking of content usage.</p>
